lead_paragraph: Honda's Dani Pedrosa became the eighth different MotoGP winner in eight races on Sunday to deny Italian great Valentino Rossi a home victory in front of 100,000 flag-waving fans at the San Marino Grand Prix.

headline.print_headline: Motorcycling: Pedrosa Denies Rossi a Home Win at Misano
